Communication with mobile android and authWS

		
	A) app/messages : type POST , format Json 
		Collect messages according to Distance and date by android mobile (button: Near Me)

		A.1) Request : 
			
			Type: Application/json

			Body 
				Example: {"longitude": "132.12", "latitude": "50.56", "radius": "35.24", "date": "12/11/17", "hours": "16.05"}
		
			Data type: 
					- Longitude : Double
					- Latitude : Double
					- Radius : Double
					- Date : String
					- Hours : String

			A.2) Response : 
			
		- HTTP status code 200 : Resultat des topics à proximité

				Return  
					Example : (String) Message OK
					
Example(Json): [message : {"longitude": "123.12", "latitude": "21.56", "popularity": "12", "date": "12/11/17", "hours": "16.05", "topic": "Rugby"}, message : {"longitude": "145.12", "latitude": "25.56", "popularity": "35", "date": "12/11/17", "hours": "13.00", "topic": "Shopping"}]



	B) app/message : type POST , format Json
		Creating a message by android mobile 

		B.1) Request : 
			
			Type: Application/json
			Head (Token : String)

			Body
				Example(Json): {"longitude": "123.12", "latitude": "21.56", "popularity": "12", "date": "12/11/17", "hours": "16.05", "topic": "Rugby"}

				Data type: 
					- Longitude : Double
					- Latitude : Double		
					- Popularity : Integer
					- Date : String
					- Hours : String
					- Topic : String


		B.2) Response : 
			
		- HTTP status code 200 : 

				Return  
					Example : (String) Message OK
			Example: {"key": "12", "message": "Message OK"}

		- HTTP status code 400 : Bad request 

				Return
					Example : (String) Error Message 

		- HTTP status code 500 :  Error Server

				Return
					Example : (String) Error Service or BDD

		- HTTP status code 501 : Error Service Authentification

				Return
					Example : (String) Error Web Service Auth

 
	C) app/mess/key : type POST , format Json
						
		Type: Application/json

			Body: 

				Example: {"id": 13}


		C.2) Response : 

			- HTTP status code 200 : Popularity was taken into account
				Return 
					Example: (String) Add popularity 

			- HTTP status code 400 : Bad request ID message 
				Return
					Example: (String) Error ID

			- HTTP status code 500 : Error Server 
				Return
					Example : (String) Error Service or BDD

			- HTTP status code 501 : Error Service Authentification
				Return
					Example : (String) Error Web Service Auth


			
				
